All Skills 100%. 100% Dicing. 100% Clan chat. 100% Nex. 100% Corporal Beast. 100% Bal'lak The Pummeller. 100% Unholy Cursebearer. 100% Jad with only 1 wave. 100% Clanwars. 100% Castle wars. 100% Barrows Money Making Way(::hunter/::thieve). When someone gets a 99 in a skill, everyone will know. 100% Dungeoneering with a points shop. You get TerrorPoints when you kill any npc, spend in the points shop. NPC's that drop rares for your chance to get your hands on. Slayer Minigame. Voting System. Custom Home. Custom Teleports. No Lag. Great Staff. 24/7(No Lag) Donator benefits with their own shop.
